title: Chip's knowledge cutoff?
content: Chip's knowledge cutoff is February 2025. This means that Chip may not have information on courses, professors, or other data beyond this date.

title: Who is Chip?
content: Chip is a chatbot designed to assist students with their questions and provide information about the Computer Science Society (CSS) at the University of Windsor. Chip is not a real person, but rather an AI program that can help you with various inquiries related to the CSS and its activities.
